TA INSTRUCTIONS

1. import the project war file into the eclipse environment

2. the database engine used is derby, create a new derby dataabase connection

3.run the createBookStoreDB script (located under the main project folder) on an SQL scrapbook

4. run the MainPage.java on the apache 8.5 server and test out the various functions of the website 

To test the SOAP and REST do the following:

1. import the RestClientTest and SOAPClientTest war files onto the eclipse interface

2. to run them run on the server

3. for the SOAP client run the SOAPClientPage.java in the package ctrl and insert the book ID

4. for the REST client run the RestClient.java in the package ctrl and insert a receipt number given after payment 
	(1 to 3 are in the database by default to test)

